Tamaziγt n Rrif akken ssawalen imezdaγ n temnaṭ n Rrif di Lmarruk, d yiwet n tantala Tamaziγt n ugafa.

Tamaziγt n Arrif neγ Tarifit neγ Tarifect sawalentt azal n 3 ar 4 imelyan n medden deg Lmarruk ugafa (Nadur, Ḥusima, Temsaman, Serwan, Tamrrict, Azenγenγan), deg tmurt n Fransa, Ḥulllan, Spanya, tamurt Uliman.. 

Tarifit d tetteki deg tarbaɛt umi seman "Taznatit" ar tama n tantala Tacawit, Tacenwit, Tanfussit.
